  "description": "Tucked within the manicured grounds of a private estate in Surrey, England, a newly completed Music Pavilion by SHH Architecture \u0026 Interiors redefines what it means to design for sound. This purpose-built structure blends refined acoustic performance with architectural elegance, creating a sanctuary tailored for a true audiophile.",
